### Day 6 – Assign Roles & Users to Platform Group

#### 1. Accessing Groups
- Opened **ServiceNow**.  
- Clicked on **All → Search for Tables**.  
- Selected **Tables** under **System Definition**.  
- Selected the **Platform Group**.  

#### 2. Assigning Users
- Under **Group Members**, clicked **Edit**.  
- Selected **Manne Niranjan**.  
- Clicked **Save**.  

#### 3. Assigning Roles
- Navigated to **Roles**.  
- Selected **Platform_role**.  
- Clicked **Save**.
